survey_response.review_text:
I met with an accident a year ago and damaged my front 3 teeth. I literally was looking for a professional and experienced dentist. 
Dr pallavi is very professional and very soft spoken as well. She understood my issues and also made me aware of some others issues which needed to be fixed. After all the fillings we proceeded for crowns. I had to visit 3 times just to give the impression of those teeth but when after so long when i got my crown i can say that i wont regret even 1% visiting 3 times. It fits perfectly well and i must say Dr pallavi’s experience really helped me here. I am extremely happy and I really wanted to write this review. One last thing, if i ever have to refer someone for any dental treatment, there’s only one Dentist i am going to refer thats “Dr Pallavi” 
Worth my time and every single rupee spent.

I went for  re-root canal treatment of my tooth and cavity fillings at Dentawell. Dr. Pallavi and her staff are very polite and highly skilled to perform any treatment. 

The doctors *** **** ************* *** will explain you case in very much detail. They will keep checking the comfort level of the patient and give proper time to complete the treatment.

I am satisfied with my treatment and would recommend Dentawell clinic for any dental and oral health related consultations.

A very nice place for all your dental problems. It was very neat and clean clinic where all the covid protocols are followed as well. All the guidance i got for my dental problem was satisfying and solved my dental issues. I highly recommend this place for any dental issue.

*** ********* *** ** ********* ** **** *****. She listens to her patient calmly and advuce them genuinely... She treats her little patients very carefully and calmly. She gives her full time to treat.. No hurries in treatment and satisfies patient queries.

We were looking for a very gentle dental care for our elderly father year and we're totally delighted with the care & understanding provided by Dr Pallavi Dhama. Further visits to the surgery were  scheduled. He was very happy with the outcome and we were very impressed by the level of understanding and care provided. Highly recommend.

My visit to Dr Pallavi went extremely smooth. She is such a calm and composed doctor that all my worries flew out the window. I am usually very scared to go to dentists but she made me feel at ease. I would highly recommend her for your dentistry needs.

I am really happy with my changed smile. I had 4 crooked front upper teeth. At this age I don't want braces. Dr. Pallavi suggested me veneers and we decided to go ahead after the necessary discussion. The result came out beautiful.  exactly what was needed. Thanks to my doctors skills and listening ear. I am very happy with Dr Pallavi and will definitely recommend her to patients who are looking for dental treatment.
